sentences: Betty Moon is a Canadian-American singer, songwriter, and producer who is currently based in Los Angeles.
In the early 1990s, she was signed to A&M Records and later started her own production company and record label, Evolver Music, Inc.
She has released eleven studio albums, including her most recent project, Undercover, in 2022.
